t's become brothers.  You be the older brother, and I'll be the \nyounger.\"", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1836", "off": 2987, "word": "don't want", "class": "I_STATE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1837", "off": 2998, "word": "to argue", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "INFINITIVE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1838", "off": 3039, "word": "let's", "class": "I_ACTION", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1839", "off": 3045, "word": "become", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1840", "off": 3067, "word": "be the older brother", "class": "STATE", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1841", "off": 3094, "word": "'ll be the \nyounger", "class": "STATE", "tense": "FUTURE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1842", "off": 3118, "word": "\"Agreed!\"", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1843", "off": 3119, "word": "Agreed", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1844", "off": 3147, "word": "said", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1845", "off": 3234, "word": "Pick", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1846", "off": 3256, "word": "grab", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1847", "off": 3280, "word": "drag", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1848", "off": 3350, "word": "went", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1849", "off": 3374, "word": "saw", "class": "PERCEPTION", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1850", "off": 3413, "word": "started", "class": "ASPECTUAL", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1851", "off": 3421, "word": "to tie", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "INFINITIVE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1852", "off": 3471, "word": "waited", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1853", "off": 3482, "word": "w